{"article_id":"oXuaqy6gdRdpclNx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump has declared a national emergency","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"in a bid","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to fund his promised wall at the US-Mexico border","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"without congressional approval ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"an action","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Democrats vowed to challenge as a violation of the US Constitution .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"The Republican president 's move","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to circumvent Congress","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"represented a new approach","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"to making good on a 2016 presidential campaign pledge","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"to halt the flow of undocumented immigrants into the country .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Trump began weighing whether to declare a national emergency","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"after Democrats refused to cave to his demand for $ 5.7bn in funding for the wall ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"prompting a 35-day government shutdown","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"- the longest in US history .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"That shutdown ended last month","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"after Trump , his fellow Republicans , and Democrats came to an agreement","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"to open the government for three weeks","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"while talks continued on border security .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Facing a Friday deadline ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"congressional leaders came to an agreement earlier this week","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"aimed at keeping the government open .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Although it includes $ 1.37bn in funding","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"to help build physical barriers on the border ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"it does not include money for concrete walls ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"forcing Trump to look elsewhere for funding .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Here 's a look at what a national emergency is ,","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"and why Democrats and many experts say","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"Trump does not have the legal authority","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"to declare one in this context .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"What is a national emergency ?","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"What will happen","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"once it 's declared ?","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"US federal law gives a number of powers to the president","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"to use in response to a `` crisis , exigency , or emergency circumstances","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"threatening the nation '' ,","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"a document","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"prepared for Congress","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"states .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"He can do so at will .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Declaring a national emergency allows the president to meet the problems of `` governing effectively '' in times of crisis .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"They also allow the president to `` seize property ,","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"organise and control the means of production ,","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"seize commodities ,","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"assign military forces abroad ,","depth":16},{"id":45,"text":"institute martial law ,","depth":17},{"id":46,"text":"seize and control all transportation and communication ,","depth":18},{"id":47,"text":"regulate the operation of private enterprise ,","depth":19},{"id":48,"text":"restrict travel ,","depth":20},{"id":49,"text":"and , in a variety of ways , control the lives of United States citizens , ''","depth":20},{"id":50,"text":"the document states .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Declaring a national emergency is a rare step .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"In this case , it would allow Trump to redirect federal funds from elsewhere","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"to pay for his border wall .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Jessica Levinson , political law professor at Loyola Law School , said","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"although Trump had the power","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"to declare an emergency at any moment ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"it would be a complicated process .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"`` He has to say","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"'here 's an emergency","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"and here 's what I need ' , ''","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"she told .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"`` I need more money ,","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"I need more people , etc , ''","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"she added .","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"`` But the question is then","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"if he waited so long","depth":16},{"id":67,"text":"to do this ,","depth":16},{"id":68,"text":"and the country went through a government shutdown over this ,","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"how is it an emergency now ?","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"Where is the urgency ? ''","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"It 's also unclear where Trump can get the funding","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"because Congress would still need to earmark money for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"However , some legal experts have told local media","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that Trump may be able to turn to unallocated funds in the Department of Defense 's budget .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"A source told Reuters","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"that the White House lawyers had vetted the figures","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"and believed","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"they would withstand a legal challenge .","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"Levinson said","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"to expect a legal battle","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"once Trump declares a national emergency .","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"`` At that point , people will sue","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"and say","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"this is not an emergency , ''","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"she said .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Fifteen Democrats in the Republican-controlled Senate introduced legislation prior to Trump 's declaration","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"to prevent Trump from invoking emergency powers","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"to transfer funds to his wall from accounts","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Congress has already committed to other projects .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"New York state 's attorney general , Letitia James , said","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"her office would also challenge Trump in court .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"Under the Constitution , Congress holds the national purse strings","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"and makes major decisions on spending taxpayer money .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Disputes over the constitutionality or legality of the exercise of emergency powers are judicially reviewable ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"the document","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"prepared for Congress","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"states .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"who campaigned on a promise","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"to build a wall on the US-Mexico border ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"had demanded Congress allocate $ 5.7bn in funding for the wall .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"But Democrats ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"who recently took control of the House of Representatives ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"refused ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"calling the wall ineffective , expensive and immoral .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"The legislation","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"hammered out by Congress this week","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"does not include money for a concrete wall ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"but it does allocate $ 1.37bn in funding for physical barriers .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"But Trump hopes","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"by ordering the national emergency","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"he can still follow through on his campaign promise .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"Trump estimated","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"his emergency declaration could free up as much as $ 8bn","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"to pay for part of the wall .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Estimates of its total cost run as high as $ 23bn .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"The president acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"that his order would face a lengthy court fight .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"`` I expect to be sued .","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"I should n't be sued ...","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"We 'll win in the Supreme Court , ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Trump predicted","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"as he announced the national emergency .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"On Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"as congressional leaders announced a compromise","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"that did n't include wall funding ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Trump declared in front of a rally of supporters","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"that he was going to get the wall built one way or the other .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"`` Just so you know -","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"we 're building the wall anyway , ''","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"The president maintains","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"that the wall is necessary","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"to stem irregular immigration and drug trafficking .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"But statistics show","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"that irregular immigration has dropped to a 20-year low","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"and that many drug shipments are likely smuggled through official ports of entry ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"leading critics to argue","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"a wall is not needed .","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Confronted with those statistics at a Rose Garden event with reporters ,","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"they were `` wrong '' .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"Democrats have long resisted Trump 's call for a wall","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"the president had fabricated a `` crisis '' at the border","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"to justify an unconstitutional grab for funding .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Nancy Pelosi , the Democratic speaker of the House of Representatives , and top Senate Democrat Chuck Schumer swiftly responded to Trump 's declaration .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"`` The president 's actions clearly violate the Congress ' s exclusive power of the purse ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"which our Founders enshrined in the Constitution , ''","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"they said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"`` The Congress will defend our constitutional authorities in the Congress , in the courts , and in the public ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"using every remedy available , \"","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"they added .","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"On Thursday , Pelosi said","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"there was no crisis at the border with Mexico","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"that requires a national emergency order .","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"`` If the president can declare an emergency on something","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"that he has created as an emergency","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"- an illusion","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"that he wants to convey -","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"just think of what a president with different values can present to the American people , ''","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"Pelosi added ,","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"pointing to gun violence in the United States as a national emergency .","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"Democrats were prepared to respond appropriately to a declaration of national emergency .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"The majority of Americans continue to oppose expanding the border wall .","depth":3},{"id":167,"text":"Of 1,505 adults","depth":5},{"id":168,"text":"surveyed last month in a Pew Research Center poll ,","depth":5},{"id":169,"text":"58 percent said","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"they opposed substantial wall expansions","depth":6},{"id":171,"text":"while 40 percent said","depth":6},{"id":172,"text":"favoured wall expansions .","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"Partisan differences are widening","depth":4},{"id":174,"text":"as Republican support for the wall is at a record high at 82 percent , an increase of 10 percent from last year ,","depth":5},{"id":175,"text":"while Democratic support has reached a new low at 6 percent , down from 13 percent last year .","depth":5},{"id":176,"text":"Although opinion over wall expansions have not seen a substantial change from last year ,","depth":4},{"id":177,"text":"they have never been more sharply divided along partisan lines .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":355,"left":343,"right":354,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":343,"left":203,"right":342,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":188,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":183,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":0,"right":182,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":180,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":1,"right":179,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":185,"right":186,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":184,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":184,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":195,"right":201,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":195,"left":191,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"